item.title: ICURFC 2nd XV: Welcome back Sylvia
item.author: Daniel Kirrane,
item.description: The first game of the 2XV’s season was a home match against Queen Mary’s, a side who last season were 2 leagues above us. Due to this theoretical gulf in quality, the Queen Mary’s side decided to turn up 45 minutes late, leaving little time for a warm up. Little did they know that this 2XV side were …
